XỬ LÝ SỰ CỐ ATTT Summary : This image displays the logo for Icetea Software, featuring a stylized red geometric emblem above the company name. logo: Icetea Software Logo Elements : • Central emblem consists of interlocking red lines forming a symmetrical, abstract geometric shape resembling the letter "S" within a diamond outline. • Two small red diamond shapes flank the central emblem horizontally. • Company name "Icetea Software" is written below the emblem; "Icetea" in light gray, "Software" in bold black font. Typography & Colour : • "Icetea" uses a thin, sans-serif font in light gray. • "Software" uses a bold, sans-serif font in black. • Emblem and diamonds are rendered in solid red (#D32F2F or similar). Layout & Dimensions : • Emblem is centered above the text. • Text is horizontally aligned, with "Icetea" and "Software" on the same line. • Logo is set against a plain white background. Analysis : • The logo combines a modern, geometric emblem with clean typography to convey a professional and technology-focused brand identity. The use of red suggests energy and confidence, while the bold "Software" emphasizes the company's core business. # Danh sách thông tin liên lạc khi xảy ra sự cố ATTT

Summary : This image displays the logo for Icetea Software, featuring a stylized red geometric emblem above the company name.

logo: Icetea Software

Logo Elements :
  • Central emblem consists of interlocking red lines forming a symmetrical, abstract geometric shape resembling the letter "S" within a diamond outline.
  • Two small red diamond shapes flank the central emblem horizontally.
  • Company name "Icetea Software" is written below the emblem; "Icetea" in light gray, "Software" in bold black font.

Typography & Colour :
  • "Icetea" uses a thin, sans-serif font in light gray.
  • "Software" uses a bold, sans-serif font in black.
  • Emblem and diamonds are rendered in solid red (#D32F2F or similar).

Layout & Dimensions :
  • Emblem is centered above the text.
  • Text is horizontally aligned, with "Icetea" and "Software" on the same line.
  • Logo is set against a plain white background.

Analysis :
  • The logo combines a modern, geometric emblem with clean typography to convey a professional and technology-focused brand identity. The use of red suggests energy and confidence, while the bold "Software" emphasizes the company's core business.
